.Thermal neutron temperature was deduced from the ratio
of cross section for reaction Lu-176(n,g)Lu-171g
in this beam to the cross-section measured in the
thermal column of BR1 rector (T=300 K).  T=313+-10 K.
.Total cross section for Eu-151 is deduced by
